mpc is a complex floating-point library with exact rounding.
It is based on the GNU MPFR floating-point library (http://www.mpfr.org/),
which is itself based on the GNU MP library (http://gmplib.org/).

注意:
    安装mpc之前请先安装 gmp和mpfr
	可以分别通过如下方式获取代码:
	git clone https://github.com/embedded-software/loongson-mpfr.git
	git clone https://github.com/embedded-software/loongson-gmp.git

	如果电脑是mips架构龙芯cpu，系统是debian，请将mpc安装到/usr目录
    即配置编译安装过程如下：
    ./configure --prefix=/usr
    make
    make check
    sudo make install
